text: The Final Destination (also known as Final Destination 4) is a 2009 American 3D supernatural horror movie directed by David R. Ellis and written by Eric Bress. It is the fourth movie in the Final Destination movie series. It stars Bobby Campo, Shantel VanSanten, and Mykelti Williamson. The movie is about a group of people after they escape a deadly accident during a stock car race, with Death stalking and killing them one by one. The Final Destination was theatrically released on August 28, 2009, by Warner Bros. Pictures and New Line Cinema. It received negative reviews from critics. The following movie in the franchise, Final Destination 5, was released in August 2011. ==References== Category:Final Destination movies Category:2009 horror movies Category:American sequel movies Category:English-language movies Category:Movies about precognition Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by David R.
